channel.title: Need help with portforwarding with AT&T

I had this work once, but then i got a new router so then im stuck on this, is anything wrong?

When i have it like this and i log in with no-ip server part it shows that server must be down but it shows this:

and when i log in regualrly with 127.0.0.1 or 0.0.0.0 it says theres 2 players online, and if i log on with no-ip twice and then it says 3 players online? need help!
